{
  "stem": "11133.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We understood there was one terrible guy, and somehow they caught him in some way and kept him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because I know that, when the Russians liberated us, they hanged him, and they wanted us all to watch the hanging.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Russians.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Russian army was a very interesting army when they came in, unlike an army that you think marches to a-- to a goose-stepping beat, you know.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were very incredible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were women, and young boys, and older men.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was just-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they weren't in ranks of any sort, they just came, you know, with one of them on a horse to start with, to tell us that we were free and to tell us to leave the camp.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, we were afraid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We did not know how to walk outside of the camp without walking in fives, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But after a while, you know, in a few days, we started back to Poland walking.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And, you know, all the bridges were blown up, and all the roads were-- it took us-- let's see now, we were liberated on the 9th, and it took us, I would say, a good two weeks to get back to Krakow.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'45, Mm-hm.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No I did not, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I understand he left at night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were some people who did accompany him, and some people who did see him leave, but I was not one of them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We walked, primarily.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We walked, or we hitched some rides or with-- on carts, if people would take us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Czechs were incredibly kind people, the kindest people I've met, really.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were wonderful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They really extended themselves.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They shared whatever they had with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Really good people.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
